@{b}Some words from the author...@{ub}

GUNBEE F-99 is the first completed videogame on any platform created in Peru
and spreaded outside the country. Other local productions back in early '90
on the Commodore 64 were also created by Twin Eagles Group (TEG).

I formed TEG with the hope to make videogames as a contribution for our
favourite computer. Unfortunately for us, in those days it was very hard to
get in contact with outside people and after a large activity in our scene
the members left the group and everything stopped. In 1997 I got an internet
account and months later I felt the need to code something funny again...
And that was the birth of 'Gunbee F-99'. Actually I'm the only member of TEG.
  
@ENDNODE
              
